txt.en: Defeat many wolves, boars, bears, deer, and moose in the Wildwood.

The Wildwood is teeming with game, both large and small. Their numbers threaten to strain the ability the land has to support them, and they pose a threat to the people who are trying to establish a foothold in the forest.
Defeat many of the big game animals in the Wildwood
